Complete this Union-Find implementation:

```
class UnionFind:
    function __init__(size):
        self.parent = [i for i in range(size)]
        self.rank = [0] * size

    function find(x):
        if self.parent[x] != x:
            _______________
        return self.parent[x]

    function union(x, y):
        px, py = self.find(x), self.find(y)
        if px == py:
            return
        if self.rank[px] < self.rank[py]:
            self.parent[px] = py
        elif self.rank[px] > self.rank[py]:
            self.parent[py] = px
        else:
            self.parent[py] = px
            self.rank[px] += 1
```

