Complete this network flow Ford-Fulkerson implementation:

```
function maxFlow(graph, source, sink):
    max_flow_value = 0

    while True:
        parent = bfs(graph, source, sink)
        if parent[sink] == -1:
            break

        // Find minimum capacity along the path
        path_flow = infinity
        s = sink
        while s != source:
            path_flow = min(path_flow, graph[parent[s]][s])
            s = parent[s]

        // Add path flow to overall flow
        max_flow_value += path_flow

        // Update residual capacities
        v = sink
        while v != source:
            u = parent[v]
            graph[u][v] -= path_flow
            _______________
            v = parent[v]

    return max_flow_value
```

