What is the recurrence relation for LCS?

```
FUNCTION LCS(X, Y, m, n):
    if m == 0 OR n == 0:
        return 0
    if X[m-1] == Y[n-1]:
        return 1 + LCS(X, Y, m-1, n-1)
    else:
        return MAX(LCS(X, Y, m, n-1), LCS(X, Y, m-1, n))
```

What is the constraint in 0/1 Knapsack problem?

```
FUNCTION Knapsack(weights, values, n, capacity):
    if n == 0 OR capacity == 0:
        return 0
    if weights[n-1] > capacity:
        return Knapsack(weights, values, n-1, capacity)
    else:
        include = values[n-1] + Knapsack(weights, values, n-1, capacity-weights[n-1])
        exclude = Knapsack(weights, values, n-1, capacity)
        return MAX(include, exclude)
```

