What is the Ford-Fulkerson method for?

```
FUNCTION FordFulkerson(graph, source, sink):
    maxFlow = 0

    while EXISTS augmentingPath FROM source TO sink:
        pathFlow = INFINITY

        // Find minimum capacity along the path
        for edge in augmentingPath:
            pathFlow = MIN(pathFlow, edge.capacity)

        // Update residual capacities
        for edge in augmentingPath:
            edge.capacity = edge.capacity - pathFlow
            edge.reverse.capacity = edge.reverse.capacity + pathFlow

        maxFlow = maxFlow + pathFlow

    return maxFlow
```

