What is a Hamiltonian Path?

```
FUNCTION FindHamiltonianPath(graph, path, pos):
    if pos == V:
        return true  // visited all vertices

    for v = 0 to V-1:
        if IsSafeVertex(v, graph, path, pos):
            path[pos] = v
            if FindHamiltonianPath(graph, path, pos + 1):
                return true
            path[pos] = -1  // backtrack

    return false

FUNCTION IsSafeVertex(v, graph, path, pos):
    // Check if vertex v can be added to path
    if graph[path[pos-1]][v] == 0:
        return false  // no edge

    for i = 0 to pos-1:
        if path[i] == v:
            return false  // already visited

    return true
```

