What is the formula for Rolling Hash?

```
FUNCTION RollingHash(text, pattern_length):
    base = 256
    mod = 101
    hash_value = 0

    // Calculate initial hash
    for i = 0 to pattern_length - 1:
        hash_value = (hash_value * base + text[i]) % mod

    // Rolling hash for remaining characters
    for i = pattern_length to LENGTH(text) - 1:
        // Remove leading character
        hash_value = (hash_value - text[i - pattern_length] * POWER(base, pattern_length - 1)) % mod
        // Add trailing character
        hash_value = (hash_value * base + text[i]) % mod

    return hash_value
```

